data.description: This stately three-bedroom one-and-a-half bathroom brick beauty in tree-lined Rosedale Park is brimming with character and charming details, from original hardwood floors and trim to beautiful leaded glass doors throughout. A sunny Florida room leads to a spacious three-season porch and large deck that offers loads of room for entertaining, gardening and play space. Currently being used as a home gym and rec room, the clean and dry basement provides additional living/hobby space. Detached 2.5 car garage. HIGHEST AND BEST DUE BY MONDAY APRIL 8TH AT 5PM.
